################################################################################
### Notes
################################################################################
# - Todas as rotas começam com /api/
# - IDs devem ser GUIDs válidos
# - O status Active é atribuído automaticamente na criação
# - Senhas são automaticamente hasheadas com SHA256
# - Senhas nunca são retornadas nas respostas




